{"tid":1034043,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯］靚女價值遠超靚仔","createTime":"2019-02-23T15:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T08:05:02.000Z","uid":137339,"like":509,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"d03d267b14f72f042699893416fcbe825263dd90","tid":1034043,"uid":137339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"係香港靚女數量係多過靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中都會係街見到靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係靚仔就相對少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常應該係物以罕為貴，靚仔應該係有價值好多，但係情況正好相反。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於當權者大多數係男人(唔計林鄭）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做到當權者嘅男人多數都係樣衰（個天好公平，讀得書嘅多數都係樣衰，而樣衰嘅人亦都能夠更專注做大事，因為唔使溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n而呢班有權力嘅人亦都會討厭靚仔，因為當佢地未有權力前就係俾靚仔搶曬啲女<br />\n<br />\n加上男人要溝女，會視靚仔過自己嘅人為競爭對手，除非係明星，因為距離差太遠，好似係學界撚唔會視英超球為假想敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上對靚女嘅渴求，有權力嘅男人自然會對優待女人，而針對靚仔。<br />\n<br />\n身邊好多靚仔都撈唔掂女都溝唔到，但係啲靚女朋友個個風生水起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：靚仔優勢小，靚女優勢大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e1c6b1691f899adde8d9a6b3fe84be40f68539","tid":1034043,"uid":182556,"like":305,"dislike":10,"score":295,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"樓豬努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等執我呢啲靚仔二灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9924641a0311f3b9214ead716f599ec426ca68d","tid":1034043,"uid":137339,"like":216,"dislike":10,"score":206,"quote":{"pid":"58e1c6b1691f899adde8d9a6b3fe84be40f68539","tid":1034043,"uid":182556,"like":305,"dislike":10,"score":295,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"樓豬努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\"